title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: When attempting to export the data from the table, an exception is thrown in the ReportEngineService.getMetaData() method.
EB: The expected behavior is that the data should be successfully exported.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Open the attached report. 2. Attempt to export the data from the table.
